      "rationale": "Validation uses the normalized index of hemolysis (NIH) as QoI, which is the same metric used in the clinical decision threshold. However, the spatial averaging procedure differs between the CFD post-processor and the experimental measurement protocol. Achieved level 2 against required level 4."
    },
    {
