    "rationale": "Despite all 13 credibility factors showing achieved levels below required levels and 6 factors flagged as unassessed epistemic gaps at MRL 5, the package is formally accepted for submission to the regulatory review pipeline pending resolution of identified gaps. The Monte Carlo UQ results provide partial uncertainty coverage. The provenance chain supporting the primary validation result is considered complete by the assessment team; the intermediate hemolysis result node is assumed to carry an implicit link to prior experimental work, though no formal IRI provenance edge was recorded.",
